Paper: hep-th/9204008

Date: 1992-04-03

Title: Self-Dual Chern-Simons Solitons with Non-Compact Groups

Authors: Daniel Cangemi

Comments: (15 double-spaced pages)

Journal-ref: J.Phys. A26 (1993) 2945-2954

It is shown how to couple non-relativistic matter with a Chern--Simons gaugefield that belongs to a non-compact group. We treat in some details the$SL(2,{\bf R})$ and the Poincar\'e $ISO(2,1)$ groups. For suitableself-interactions, we are able to exhibit soliton solutions.